Class Summary
ClasspathNutDao A NutDao implementation for classpath accesses.
DiskNutDao A NutDao implementation for disk accesses.
HttpNutDao A NutDao implementation for HTTP accesses.
PathNutDao A NutDao implementation for accesses based on the path API provided by WUIC.
ProxyNutDao Internal NutDao class that maps particular path to a particular Nut when the NutDao.create(String) method is invoked.
 

Package com.github.wuic.nut.dao.core Description

Package where NutDao implementations are defined for core module.

HTTP, DISK and CLASSPATH strategies are supported here.
